{"word":"G4075 - πετρώδης - petrṓdēs - pet-ro'-dace - Stony","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πετρώδης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">petrṓdēs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pet-ro'-dace</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Stony</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கற்பாறையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"rocky, stony"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4073 - πέτρα - pétra - pet'-ra/4073\">G4073</a> and <a href=\"#/G1491 - εἶδος - eîdos - i'-dos/1491\">G1491</a>; <i>rock like</i>, that is, <i>rocky:</i> - stony.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}